snippet.title: Bunny Hill - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Bunny Hill is up on Steam!  
Store Link: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1424350/Bunny_Hill/

After 7 months of solo development and collaborating with Gupi for the banger soundtrack, Bunny Hill is releasing on Steam on October 23rd. Go wish list it if you like it, it helps me out a lot! I am very happy with the project and how it turned out, all of the final polish really brings it all together. 

Thank you all for watching the process.

find me here: https://www.instagram.com/roar.tea/
